Graduates Bachelor/Master/MBA Degree in Finance / Banking/ Mathematics;
Possession of CMA/CFA/FRM (completed or in progress) is a plus;
At least 1 years’ experience working in commercial bank or Big4, preferably in Finance fields and/or Risk fields.

